ActMinistries and Ministers of State Act
SubjectOrder Terminating the Assignment of the Honourable Helena Jaczek and Assigning the Honourable Filomena Tassi to Assist the Minister of Industry
PrecisOrder (1) terminating the assignment of the the Honourable HELENA JACZEK, made by Order in Council P.C.2021-917 of October 26, 2021; and (2) assigning the Honourable FILOMENA TASSI, Minister of State (Federal Economic Development Agency for Southern Ontario) to assist the Minister of Industry in the carrying out of that Minister’s responsibilities.
